<p>Transparency in NFT means you can see all transaction facts. This is part of what a Nonfungible token is.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">How does transparency tie to the idea of decentralization?</h3>



<p>The process of decentralization backs up transparency. No single group runs it so everyone sees the same facts.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Why is transparency important for an NFT?</h3>



<p>Transparency makes sure that all activity and trades around an NFT are clear and honest.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Are all Tokenized assets transparent like NFTs?</h3>



<p>Yes, all tokenized assets like nonfungible tokens have built-in transparency because of how blockchain works.</p>
